{"type": "article", "id": 47627, "title": "贝嫂品牌估值 1 亿英镑，以及，隈研吾设计沙发系列 | 浮华日报", "description": "我们为你挑选了今天最重要和最好看的新闻。", "date": "2017-11-27T03:35:53Z", "super_tag": "", "tags": [{"id": 3322, "name": "Givenchy"}, {"id": 1619, "name": "VR"}, {"id": 2145, "name": "Converse"}, {"id": 2120, "name": "开云"}, {"id": 1980, "name": "Topshop"}, {"id": 2836, "name": "Victoria Beckham"}, {"id": 45811, "name": "A$AP Nast"}, {"id": 893, "name": "隈研吾"}], "category": 19, "column": 8, "author": 699895, "comment_count": 1, "praise_count": 285, "image": "img/article/article_show/20171127101321oD6x9RHaN2OB0XMv.jpg", "contents": "<h3 finallycleanhtml=\"true\" nocleanhtml=\"true\">一些重要的新闻：</h3><p><a href=\"http://us.fashionnetwork.com/news/Topshop-gets-another-exec-from-luxury-sector-Cuthbertson-named-design-chief,895574.html#.WhtnNLT1WgQ\" rel=\"nofollow\"><strong>Topshop 任命新的设计总监</strong></a> | Topshop 找来在奢侈品行业有长期工作经验的 Anthony Cuthbertson 担任设计总监。 他 之前在 Just Cavalli、Sass &amp; Bide 做创意总监，并担任过 Victoria Beckham 和 Mulberry 的创意顾问。Anthony Cuthbertson 将于 1 月 2 日正式上任，管理由 72 个员工组成的设计部门。</p><p><a href=\"http://us.fashionnetwork.com/news/Extended-Kering-Group-poised-to-buy-control-of-Courreges,895300.html#.WhtnTLT1WgQ\" rel=\"nofollow\"><strong>开云要买下有 56 年历史的法国女装品牌 Courrèges</strong></a> | 据报道，开云集团有意扩大旗下的品牌组合，成立于 1961 年的法国女装品牌 Courrèges 或将是下一个收购目标。不过，该品牌已经处于亏损状态，年销售额只有 2000 万。</p><p><a href=\"http://wwd.com/business-news/financial/neo-investment-partners-takes-minority-stake-victoria-beckham-11056646/\" rel=\"nofollow\"><strong>Victoria Beckham 的品牌估值 1 亿英镑</strong></a> | 英国私募基金 Neo Investment Partners 斥资 3000 万英镑，收购了贝嫂同名个人品牌 Victoria Beckham 的少数股权。目前，该品牌的估值超过了 1 亿英镑。</p><h3>一些值得一看的：</h3><p>如果<a href=\"https://www.designboom.com/design/givenchy-vr-goggles-concept-fashion-augmented-reality-11-24-2017/\" rel=\"nofollow\"> Givenchy </a>也要做 VR 智能眼镜，那么它应该长这样——来自韩国的设计工作 PDF haus，为 Givenchy 设想了一副 VR 眼镜的结构，它有着与奢侈品眼镜结合的时髦外形，绚丽的色彩，来看看： </p><div class=\"com-insert-images multiple\"><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20171127110726RF0JuYAptCUEIK1T.jpg\" data-ratio=\"0.624694\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/201711271107326h0cdCa2tRAjXuwT.jpg\" data-ratio=\"0.667482\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20171127110726fX7VbYIBOW5CaT8p.jpg\" data-ratio=\"0.624694\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20171127110726WhVpsJlaeQLwStU9.jpg\" data-ratio=\"0.541565\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/201711271107260KT2jpxoyZURGOqi.jpg\" data-ratio=\"0.624694\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20171127110726Jm9qx2N0l7rchRWe.jpg\" data-ratio=\"0.514670\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20171127110726PuKpsBrkDciUtby8.jpg\" data-ratio=\"0.666259\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure></div><p>主打天然生物的意大利有机洗护品牌 Organic Way，将在明年年初发布首款 edp 香水系列 <a href=\"https://www.oway.it/en/#organic-way/2\" rel=\"nofollow\">Own way</a>。 </p><p>这款香水的原料 100% 来自天然的花木、果物，香水瓶特意用了漆黑的玄武岩制成，还挺特别的。 </p><div class=\"com-insert-images multiple\"><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20171127110643pvxHfVhiNI7GJs63.jpg\" data-ratio=\"0.666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20171127110643Nm5qE6xZMWe4ghaD.jpg\" data-ratio=\"1.418440\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20171127110643RpQudtESZs4Ll8F9.jpg\" data-ratio=\"0.666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20171127110643it5A9YXZhgpW7KPH.jpg\" data-ratio=\"1.500000\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure></div><p>隈研吾为日本家具品牌 TIME &amp; STYLE 设计了一个的沙发系列。该系列共包括 <a href=\"https://www.fashionsnap.com/news/2017-11-26/kumakengo-timeandstyle-sofa/\" rel=\"nofollow\">KA、FU、MA </a>这三款沙发，价格均在 30 万日元以上，将于明年 1 月 中旬开始逐步发售。 </p><p>另外，隈研吾之前设计的边桌 TS、DI、FL 也将重新发售。</p><div class=\"com-insert-images multiple\"><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/201711271105144euOrCi0J3hDRYqc.jpg\" data-ratio=\"0.668182\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20171127110515kRILDapFYeZm64W2.jpg\" data-ratio=\"0.668182\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/201711271105149x0yOmkalEws63X2.jpg\" data-ratio=\"0.666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20171127110514nPRykUKLjdhAYloZ.jpg\" data-ratio=\"1.498485\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/201711271105165i4PCrQuhG9KcoEe.jpg\" data-ratio=\"0.666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20171127110516NMkF7tmOcEXUVBqK.jpg\" data-ratio=\"0.666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20171127110517noIBDjbNQ28MJZCc.jpg\" data-ratio=\"0.666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20171127110517FmudN81nMOlp2SsK.jpg\" data-ratio=\"1.498485\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20171127110516GN53HE04kRWFqmnM.jpg\" data-ratio=\"0.668182\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20171127110656z2cTEQ76wdajAtRh.jpg\" data-ratio=\"0.668182\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20171127110517E5J3Z8LTIdY2zSBl.jpg\" data-ratio=\"0.668182\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20171127110513uF6jnvHlkpT0Rc9h.jpg\" data-ratio=\"0.666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/201711271105135fea3XJSlOgQMCt1.jpg\" data-ratio=\"0.666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20171127110513iFvJfpcuIYABzENX.jpg\" data-ratio=\"0.666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20171127110514LDiw0cr6hBonuSYG.jpg\" data-ratio=\"0.666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20171127110518JCy53LEkgDcQMpR8.jpg\" data-ratio=\"0.666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure></div><p><a href=\"https://www.highsnobiety.com/p/stussy-champion-fw17-collection-buy/#slide-2\" rel=\"nofollow\">Stüssy &amp; Champion USA </a> 2017 秋冬联名系列出炉，看起来很舒服的样子。</p><div class=\"com-insert-images multiple\"><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20171127110447vOZouyx65Jztm2ci.jpg\" data-ratio=\"0.666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20171127110448tgWYu4MAHhGwKDsn.jpg\" data-ratio=\"0.666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20171127110451Vkc2eyTYCvpHMsXP.jpg\" data-ratio=\"0.666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure></div><p>美国时间 27 日上午九点，说唱歌手 A$AP Nast 与 Converse 合作的联名系列将正式上架。 </p><p>这个系列包括售价 99.99 美元的帆布鞋、不到 40 美元的 T 恤等，仅限<a href=\"https://www.footlocker.com/_-_/keyword-converse?SID=8259&amp;cm_mmc=Linkshare-_-Deeplink-_-Text-_-Footlocker\" rel=\"nofollow\">网络</a>发售。 </p><div class=\"com-insert-images multiple\"><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/201711271104010P6EVYgarfLBhMCb.jpg\" data-ratio=\"0.666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20171127110400GS7CrKwDlYfhU8dP.jpg\" data-ratio=\"0.666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/201711271103556dJv2AotHM1ElTI8.jpg\" data-ratio=\"0.666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20171127110357s2bFd4X0rx9jMn6f.jpg\" data-ratio=\"0.666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20171127110359HWtvCLb5P7mK3ois.jpg\" data-ratio=\"0.666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20171127110401UF9Ktx5jhVBNoae6.jpg\" data-ratio=\"0.666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/201711271104007m1ZQgxwHWdC9YGj.jpg\" data-ratio=\"0.666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20171127110359ockFKnWD19r30UJH.jpg\" data-ratio=\"0.666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20171127110359WGzMimHTD3BY15ja.jpg\" data-ratio=\"0.666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20171127110400Zu2gdCOkDylzs0pA.jpg\" data-ratio=\"0.666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure></div><p><br></p><p>题图来自：PDF haus</p>"}